That's a great start on Jool, looks awesome.

This might be borderline heresy, but I think it might look even better if it wasn't all green. Green should definitely be the dominant color, but some accents and highlights in yellowish or brownish hues would make it look less like "Jupiter through a green filter".

Just some feedback, I would be happy with it as shown, too.

Edit: LOL, my four year old saw it on the screen and said "It's a green Jupiter!"

Edited November 5, 2015 by Red Iron Crown
